sub new {
  my $self = shift; my $class = ref($self) || $self;
  my ($equation,$name,$ref) = @_;
  my $def = $equation->{context}{variables}{$name};
  bless {name => $name, ref => $ref, def => $def, equation => $equation}, $class;
}
